> Coming from a background in restoring Chevys, I can tell you for a
fact
> that VW people are a breed unto themselves.  Chevy people, and maybe
all
> other car people, have absolutely no interest in helping their
fellow
> collectors, restorers, etc.  They keep all of their sources for
parts,
> information, etc, a secret.  With those cars, it's every man for
